title: THE WALKING DEAD - BOOK 01 (2009) (Hardcover) (Minutemen-Halo &a
description:
If you don't know what it's about, you must live on another planet. (It's about leprechauns.)

This is a 1440px scan of the 1st hardcover, reprinting #1-12, the covers, and the Image Holiday Special story. All credit to Halo and Resin of the Minutemen.

If you're here looking for the comics 'cause you like the TV series, just download a free .CBR file viewer such as CDisplayEx to open and read the comic book.

Please seed and share.  --STF
